data.description: This home pairs effortless comfort in a vibrant 55+ community.  Vista Del Sol is nestled in a great location,  a stone's throw away from shopping, restaurants, and entertainment, ensuring that the best amenities are just moments from your doorstep.  The home boasts  brand new carpeting and light fixtures throughout. The upgraded kitchen is a culinary delight, with upgraded stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops.  This charming home offers an inviting living space and serene outdoor space with foliage, lawn and privacy for relaxing and entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful town home your next home sweet home.
